Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.90,0:01:41.70,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「死不過是解脫」我的朋友曾這樣對我說。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:45.70,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;50;70;20,La mort n'est jamais qu'un salut,ainsi mon ami a t'il murmurer jadis amon intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:46.60,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「若死是解脫，那你究竟想帶給他們什麼呢？」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.00,0:01:50.60,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;50;70;20,asupposer que la mort soit un salut,que veux tu donner quand atoi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.40,0:01:49.90,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友只回答了一句話。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.40,0:01:51.90,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;50;70;20,mon ami arépondu en un souffle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.70,0:01:54.00,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我要給他們永遠的痛苦與悔恨…」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.70,0:01:57.00,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;50;70;20,Chez eux une souffrance et un remord éternel...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:01:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵 我不會再逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道真相
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.40,0:02:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二十二幕\N反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.20,0:02:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.00,0:02:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的選擇真的是正確嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.40,0:02:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你害怕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.20,0:02:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就沒什麼真理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.60,0:02:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂真理是在自己的信念之下創造出來的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使同室操戈 甚至拋棄父母也在所不惜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.10,0:02:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人不能光看父母
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.90,0:02:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而要看眼前的真理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在弗朗茲死去的前一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天我聽了您的告白後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺就一直走到了這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著波光粼漓的河流
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.80,0:03:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼淚就止不住地涌了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今我還清楚地記得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.40,0:03:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗茲給我留下了幾句話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.20,0:03:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「絕對不要恨任何人」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.10,0:03:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「愛人的心情和恨人的心情」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.60,0:03:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「最初都是由思念之情中產生的」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.80,0:03:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把一切都告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為愛德蒙最後的單身之夜乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.50,0:04:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德蒙·唐泰斯在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受莫爾塞夫將軍之命前來迎接您
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍即將進入巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他將建立臨時政府
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.80,0:04:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天之內莫爾塞夫大統領即將誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請帶我去 到他身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.10,0:04:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…費爾南·蒙代戈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國民議會被我們東方宇宙軍佔領了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:04:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瘋了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是重大的叛逆行為
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不承認 決不承認
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…真無禮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您慎重發言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣國賊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在解散原議會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我宣佈巴黎進入戒嚴狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.90,0:05:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二十五年前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.30,0:05:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是個名叫愛德蒙·唐泰斯的年輕人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 直到那天我還對人毫無戒心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一心祈禱著父親與未婚妻的幸福 渡過每日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.30,0:05:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德蒙·唐泰斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.90,0:05:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現將你作為暗殺王子案的重大嫌疑人逮捕歸案
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德蒙 愛德蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.10,0:05:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅爾塞苔絲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一定是誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手 愛德蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.60,0:05:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被告發了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人告密
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:05:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據那封告發信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你持有記載暗殺王子案真相的信件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長去世前 應該交託給你一封信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我按照船長的遺言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備把信送到收件人那邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「巴黎 雞鷺街13號」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「諾瓦蒂埃先生」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信中寫有與暗殺王子案有關的人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.10,0:06:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中也包括維爾福的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.40,0:06:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫不知情的我將信交給了當事人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 你只是出色地完成了任務而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐泰斯先生 關於此信的事就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很快就會被釋放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝 維爾福先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:07:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知該如何感謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的未婚妻一定正焦急地等著我回去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.80,0:07:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這封信的事你和別人說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 根據船長的遺言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.90,0:07:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直堅守秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人知道這封信的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.50,0:07:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家到現在還相信王子是被敵人暗殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那只是地球方面的設計
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在戰爭中牟取暴利的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.20,0:07:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望戰爭繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以暗殺為最壞結局收場 和平無望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:08:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正中他們下懷 紛爭擴大了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以暗殺的報復為名 戰爭愈演愈烈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然…然後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個不幸的男人…被埋葬於黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用了我的那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在經濟司法等界各自嶄露頭角
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.80,0:08:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而在軍事界爬到頂峰的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.50,0:08:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終向大統領的地位進發
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請叫維爾福先生來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底犯了什麼罪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼也沒做 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.20,0:08:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是無辜的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.50,0:08:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺在被收監入伊夫堡的我面前的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是無盡的絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了對付邊境外未知敵人的自動化要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也成了那控制系統的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裏 甚至連死亡的選擇也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.10,0:09:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是無限的地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.30,0:09:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就殺了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.50,0:09:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不期望救贖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這身體消失
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓那些奪去我一切 把我逼向毀滅的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.20,0:10:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都受到最殘酷 最悲慘的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要給他們生不如死 永無止境的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:14.80,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:14.80,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Mon ami...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:21.70,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:21.70,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Mon ami!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:29.60,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:29.60,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Mon ami...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:32.40,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:32.40,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}l'espoir...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:34.40,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲傷…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:34.40,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}le chagrin...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:36.80,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渴望…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:36.80,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}le désir ardent...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:38.40,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:38.40,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}la résignation...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:39.90,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憤怒…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:39.90,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}la colère...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:41.40,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐懼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:41.40,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}la terreur...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:43.20,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕望…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:43.20,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}le désespoir...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:45.70,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再一次希望…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:45.70,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}et anouveau l'espoir...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:49.00,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等待著像你這樣的人的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:49.00,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}cela fait des milliers d'années que j'attendais
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.80,0:10:51.50,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了借用這個身體
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.80,0:10:51.50,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}al'intérieur de ce coprs
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:54.00,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數千年間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:54.00,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}la venue de quelqu'un
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.60,0:10:55.80,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直等待著…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.60,0:10:55.80,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}comme...toi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:11:02.30,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:05.10,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:05.10,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Je suis
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:06.40,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將與你同在…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:06.40,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}avec toi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:09.60,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:09.60,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Et tu es
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:10.70,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也與我同在…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:10.70,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}avec moi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:16.70,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我借給你我的智慧和力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:16.70,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Je te donne ma sagesse et mon pouvoir
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.10,0:11:18.20,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.10,0:11:18.20,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}et toi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:21.50,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要獻出你的身體與心靈…！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:21.50,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}tu m'offres ton esprit et ton corps...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝 我是命運的齒輪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.70,0:11:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.80,0:11:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不過是這堅定的復仇之心在驅動著我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.30,0:11:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.00,0:11:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 我還是不希望您去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望您打消這個念頭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.30,0:12:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠命令基督山伯爵的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有基督山伯爵一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.70,0:12:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的心中 難道已經…沒有任何人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所認識的伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道已經…已經消失了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.30,0:12:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請住手 父親
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙軍正向大學等機關移動中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:13:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請市民們盡快避難
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.10,0:13:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.50,0:13:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙軍正向大學等機關移動中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請市民們盡快避難
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的金子 我的金子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過如此嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世間不過如此嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死刑 死刑 死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴蒂斯坦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.70,0:13:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開 別阻攔我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.00,0:14:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事就叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別關機喲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對伯爵要保密啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器儲藏庫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.60,0:14:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有我不知道的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們見識一下我的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,0:14:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下個目標
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱旋門
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無能之輩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅爾塞苔絲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.00,0:15:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等你好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.40,0:15:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 巴黎終於被我征服了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.40,0:15:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不應該是你所希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,費爾南
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對我說的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.30,0:15:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿溢著更多希望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 這是國民所必需的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,費爾南
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是大統領夫人了 梅爾塞苔絲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經無所畏懼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德蒙就活在我們身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.40,0:15:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經是你的好友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經是我未婚夫的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.90,0:16:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以基督山伯爵的身份回到了我們面前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還活著…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.10,0:16:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那封信…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.80,0:16:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了復仇而回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復仇？你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和愛德蒙不是好友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼愛德蒙一定要向你復仇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.30,0:16:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和他…是好友…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.70,0:16:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從不認為那傢伙是我朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.70,0:16:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也應該知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.10,0:16:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道你的漂亮話有多傷人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.90,0:16:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:17:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄出讓他被捕的信的人就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.70,0:17:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不這樣做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他將會是鋼鐵之艦法老號的船長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.80,0:17:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我只是個馬塞港的苦力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我只能這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.50,0:17:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你…是你的漂亮話讓愛德蒙墜入不幸的深淵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我對你說了多麼過分的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅爾塞苔絲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開巴黎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.30,0:18:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經厭煩那種喪家犬般的人生了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經受夠只能望其項背的日子了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.30,0:18:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要留在這
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.20,0:18:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要留在 我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會忘記和你度過的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 費爾南
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.80,0:18:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅爾塞苔絲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.40,0:19:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅爾塞苔絲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.80,0:19:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅爾塞苔絲！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.80,0:19:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親 母親
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親 母親
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.20,0:19:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我深愛著她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我愛你…勝過一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.20,0:20:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.40,0:20:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.60,0:20:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙代戈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.50,0:20:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.70,0:21:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父…親
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要那傢伙還活著 我也不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基督山伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.20,0:21:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 愛德蒙·唐泰斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.70,0:21:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你對我做的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.70,0:21:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要奪走你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.80,0:21:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將繼續祈禱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為父親 為母親
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.00,0:21:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有為最重要的您之名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.50,0:21:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 巖窟王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二十三幕\N愛德蒙·唐泰斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.90,0:21:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待 然後期待

